darkUI is a fork of MinUI (MinUI) by Shaun Inman
(https://github.com/shauninman/MinUI).

Upstream publishes no license file. The author states in the upstream
README: "Please feel free to fork or learn from any of my repos."
This fork exists under that permission, with full attribution; all
launcher and frontend design and engineering is Shaun Inman's work.

Release zips additionally bundle libretro cores built from their
respective upstream repositories; each core remains under its own
license (predominantly GPL). Sources are listed in workspace/all/cores/makefile and workspace/rg35xx/cores/makefile.
